               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Image of the Trinity, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from = "1r" to = "38v"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                     <note>Arranged for days of the week.  Abbadie, 244, f. 13r, Conti Rossini, ‎Notice, no. 106; Strelcyn, Lincei, no. 53 and 62; EMML 1170.
                       See <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሰይፈ፡ ሥላሴ። ወመልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለአብ።</foreign> Täsfa ‎Press, Addis Ababa 1947 EC. ‎</note>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                       <locus from = "1r" to = "5r"/>
                       <title>Introduction, intended for Monday (?, not so marked).</title>

                         <msItem xml:id="msi_1.1.1">
                           <locus from = "1r"/>
                           <title>
                         The prayer ‎to the Trinity, “I take refuge”, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ተማኅፀንኩ፡</foreign>‎</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           <locus target = "#1r"/>በስመ፡ አብ፡...፩አምላክ፡ እነቅህ፡ ወእትነሣእ፡ በቅድስት፡ ሥላሴ፡ እንዘ፡ አአምን፡ ወእትመኃፀን፡...አሜን፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡...
                           <locus target = "2r"/>ሰላም፡ ለአብ፡ ነቅአ፡ ዘይት፡ ምህረተ፡ ጥሉል፡ ሰላም፡ ለወልድ፡ ነቅአ፡ ዘይተ፡ ምህረት፡ ጥሉል፡...</incipit>
                           </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.2">
                         <locus from ="4v"/>
                         <title>Miracle of the Trinity</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ ለአብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በረከተ፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡...አሜን፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ አተዉ፡ ውስተ፡ ገጸ፡ አርያም፡ አብኒ፡ ይቤ፡ ወሀለውኒ፡ ይቤ፡ ጊዜ፡ ይመጽእ፡ ቃልየ፡ ወይትሌአል፡....
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                       <locus from = "5v" to = "7v"/>
                       <title>Tuesday</title>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                         <locus from = "5v"/>
                         <title>Prayer</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           አሐትም፡ ፍጽምየ፡ በመለኮተ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐትም፡ ከዋላየ፡ በመለኮተ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡...
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                         <locus from = "6v"/>
                          <title>Miracle</title>
                          <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                            ተአምራቲሆሙ፡...አሜን፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ በፈለገ፡ ጸቃውዕ፡
                          </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                       <locus from = "7v" to = "11v"/>
                       <title>Wednesday</title>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                         <locus from = "7v"/>
                         <title>Prayer</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ህቡረ፡ ሀሎ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡...
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                         <locus from = "11r"/>
                         <title>Miracle</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           ተአምራቲሆሙ፡...አሜን፡ ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡...
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                       <locus from = "11v" to = "17r"/>
                       <title>Thursday</title>
                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.1">
                         <locus from = "11v"/>
                         <title>Prayer</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩በግጻዌ፡ ሥሉስ፡ በሥላሴ፡ ግጽው፡ ሳህድ፡ አምላክ፡...
                         </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.2">
                           <locus from = "16v"/>
                           <title>Miracle</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                              ተአምራቲሆሙ፡...አሜን፡ ወሀሎ፡ ፩መኰንን፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡ ወአሐተ፡ አዘዘ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡ ሠራዊቱ፡...
                           </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                         <locus from = "17r" to = "23v"/>
                         <title>Friday</title>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.1">

                           <title>Prayer</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                             <locus from = "17r"/>አይ፡ ልሳን፡ ወአይ፡ ከናፍር፡ ዘይክል፡ ነቢበ፡ ዕበየ፡ ግንሮሙ፡...<locus from = "19r"/>ስብሐት፡ ለሥላሴ፡ ፈጣሪየ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለሥላሴ፡ ንጉሥየ፡...
                           </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.2">
                           <locus from = "23r"/>
                           <title>Miracle</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                             ተአምራቲሆሙ፡...ወ፡ አይ፡ ከናፍር፡ ወአይ። ልቡና፡...አሜን፡ ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወአግረሩ፡ ላዕለ፡ መንበሮሙ፡...
                           </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                         <locus from = "23v" to = "27r"/>
                         <title>Saturday</title>
                         <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6.1">
                           <locus from = "23v"/>
                           <title>Greeting to the love of the Trinity</title>
                           <note>Chaîne, Répertoire, no. 214</note>
                           <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                             ሰላም፡ ለፍቅር፡ መለኮት፡ በትስብእቱ፡ ዘጾመ፡ እንበይነ፡ ዘ[አ]ርአያሁ፡ ከመ፡ የሀበነ፡ ሰላም፡ ለፍቅረ፡ መለኮት፡ ዘይጼአን፡ ላዕለ፡ ሰረገላ፡ ኪሩቤል፡...
                           </incipit>
                         </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                         <locus from = "27r" to = "33v"/>
                         <title>Sunday</title>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           አኀሥሥ፡ ጽድቀ፡ ዘእምኀቤከ፡ ኦቀመረ፡ ጽድቅ፡...
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>
                       </msItem>

                       <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                         <locus from = "33v" to = "38v"/>
                         <title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2736RepCh20"/>
                         <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                           ሰላም፡ ለህላዌክሙ፡ ዘይመውዕ፡ ህላውያተ። ለረኪበ፡ ስሙ፡ ኅቡዕ፡ አመ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ተምኔተ።
                         </incipit>
                       </msItem>

               </msContents>
